sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 用户浏览器
    participant Nginx as Nginx
    participant React as React App
    participant API as Express API
    participant DB as MySQL

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
    Note over User,DB: 场景1: 前端页面加载流程
    User->>Nginx: GET /
    Nginx->>User: 返回 index.html + JS/CSS
    User->>React: Reacthydrate/渲染
    React->>React: Router匹配 "/" → HomePage
    React->>API: GET /api/v1/categories
    API->>DB: SELECT * FROM categories ORDER BY sort_order
    DB-->>API: 返回系列数据
    API-->>React: {code:0, data: [...]}
    React->>API: GET /api/v1/settings?key=stats_data
    API->>DB: SELECT * FROM site_settings WHERE key='stats_data'
    DB-->>API: 返回设置
    API-->>React: {code:0, data: {...}}
    React->>React: 渲染 HeroSection + EndorsementSection + ProductSeriesSection + StatsSection + CooperationCTA
    React->>User: 完整首页呈现
    User->>React: 点击产品系列卡片
    React->>React: Router导航到 /products?categoryId=1
    React->>API: GET /api/v1/products?categoryId=1
    API->>DB: SELECT * FROM products WHERE category_id=1
    DB-->>API: 返回产品列表
    API-->>React: {code:0, data: {list:[...], total:5}}
    React->>User: 产品列表页渲染
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
    Note over User,DB: 场景2: 后台内容管理流程
    participant Admin as 管理员
    participant React2 as React Admin
    participant API2 as Express API
    participant MW as Auth中间件
    participant DB2 as MySQL

    Admin->>React2: 访问 /admin/login
    Admin->>React2: 输入用户名密码 → 点击登录
    React2->>API2: POST /api/v1/auth/login {username, password}
    API2->>DB2: SELECT * FROM admin_users WHERE username=?
    DB2-->>API2: 返回用户记录
    API2->>API2: bcrypt.compare验证密码
    API2->>API2: jwt.sign生成token
    API2-->>React2: {code:0, data:{token:"xxx", user:{...}}}
    React2->>React2: localStorage存储token，跳转/admin

    Admin->>React2: 点击"新增产品" → 填写表单
    React2->>API2: POST /api/v1/admin/upload/image (multipart + Bearer token)
    API2->>MW: 验证JWT
    MW-->>API2: 认证通过
    API2->>API2: multer保存文件 → uploads/
    API2-->>React2: {code:0, data:{url:"/uploads/products/xxx.jpg"}}
    React2->>API2: POST /api/v1/admin/products {name, model, images, params}
    API2->>DB2: INSERT INTO products + product_images + product_params
    DB2-->>API2: 插入成功
    API2-->>React2: {code:0, data:{id:1}}
    React2->>Admin: 提示创建成功
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
    Note over User,DB: 场景3: 用户咨询提交流程
    participant User2 as 前台用户
    participant React3 as React前端
    participant API3 as Express API
    participant DB3 as MySQL
    participant AdminBack as 管理员后台

    User2->>React3: 浏览产品详情页 → 点击"咨询"
    React3->>User2: 弹出 InquiryDialog
    User2->>React3: 填写姓名/电话/留言 → 提交
    React3->>React3: 前端校验（必填项/手机号格式）
    React3->>API3: POST /api/v1/inquiries {name, phone, message, intentionType, productId}
    Note over API3: 公开接口，无需JWT
    API3->>API3: express-validator校验参数
    API3->>DB3: INSERT INTO inquiries
    DB3-->>API3: 插入成功
    API3-->>React3: {code:0, message:"提交成功"}
    React3->>User2: 显示"提交成功"

    AdminBack->>API3: GET /api/v1/admin/inquiries (带JWT)
    API3->>DB3: SELECT * FROM inquiries ORDER BY created_at DESC
    DB3-->>API3: 返回留言列表
    API3-->>AdminBack: 留言数据
    AdminBack->>API3: PUT /api/v1/admin/inquiries/1 {status:"processing"}
    API3->>DB3: UPDATE inquiries SET status='processing'
    DB3-->>API3: 更新成功
    API3-->>AdminBack: 更新成功
    end
